                <h3>About <span class="clrBlue">LAM</span> Conference</h3>

                <p>
                    Life after McPherson University Conference (LAM) is a 
                    student empowerment conference tailored to educate 
                    students on Life After School, what to expect after 
                    graduation and how they can maximize their stay 
                    on campus.
                </p>
                
            </div>
