            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="aims flex">
            <h3>Aims of <span class="clrBlue">LAM</span> Conference</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>To equip students to be better versions of themselves and take charge of their lives.</li>
                <li>To give them an insight into the world outside the four walls of a university.</li>
                <li>To help students chart a path for their future while on campus.</li>
                <li>To enable students to prepare for the life after school and the labor market at large.</li>
                <li>To help students position themselves for internship opportunities</li>
